\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 An exhaustive knowledge base has been constructed to systematically organize the structural, neurobiological, and philosophical frameworks required to conceptualize a next-generation AI architecture inspired by 
\f1\i \uc0\u346 abd\u257 dvaita
\f0\i0 , 
\f1\i Bh\uc0\u257 ttra
\f0\i0 , and 
\f1\i Navya-Ny\uc0\u257 ya
\f0\i0 .\
The following deep architectural breakdown outlines the mechanics of moving beyond standard vector-quantized text-audio alignment pipelines toward an intrinsic, process-oriented, and epistemically validated semantic stack.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 I. Structural Synthesis: AI vs. Neuroscience vs. Dar\uc0\u347 ana\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 To establish a coherent architecture, we map the structural primitives of contemporary Audio Large Language Models (ALMs) against the functional dynamics of human auditory cognition and the formal semantic workflows of Sanskrit epistemology.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

