\f2\b \cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 1. Architectural Primitives\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Current Audio LLMs:
\f0\b0  Treat audio as a sequence of discrete acoustic tokens (e.g., EnCodec, SoundStream) projected into a flat latent space via an adapter module. The model operates on an interleaved sequence of speech and text tokens ($t_1, a_1, a_2, t_2$), executing autoregressive next-token prediction via standard cross-attention. Semantics are purely distributional, emerging out of conditional token probabilities $P(X_n \\mid X_\{<n\})$.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Neurobiology:
\f0\b0  Continuous acoustic pressure waves strike the cochlea, which projects tonotopically to the Primary Auditory Cortex ($A1$). $A1$ and surrounding belt areas execute a dual-stream multi-timescale temporal decomposition: theta-band oscillations ($3-8\\text\{ Hz\}$) segment the stream into syllabic chunks, while gamma-band oscillations ($25-40\\text\{ Hz\}$) capture fast phonemic transitions. This signal is fed into the Default Mode Network (DMN), which maintains a persistent, low-frequency internal monologue that functions as a running situational model.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Sanskrit Dar\uc0\u347 ana:
\f0\b0  Bhart\uc0\u7771 hari\'92s 
\f1\i \uc0\u346 abd\u257 dvaita
\f0\i0  establishes 
\f1\i \uc0\u346 abda-tattva
\f0\i0  (Word-Essence) as the fundamental substratum of all awareness (
\f1\i caitanya
\f0\i0 ). Sound transitions through four levels of abstraction:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1
\f1\i \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Vaikhar\uc0\u299 :
\f0\i0  The physical, acoustic articulation (waveforms/spectrograms).\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f1\i \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Madhyam\uc0\u257 :
\f0\i0  The mental, internal sequential speech pattern (inner monologue/DMN narrative).\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f1\i \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Pa\uc0\u347 yant\u299 :
\f0\i0  The unified, non-sequential flash of conceptual meaning (
\f1\i Spho\uc0\u7789 a
\f0\i0 ).\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f1\i \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Par\uc0\u257 :
\f0\i0  The unmanifest, transcendent consciousness.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Cognition does not decode symbols post-hoc; rather, consciousness is inherently structured by 
\f1\i \uc0\u346 abda
\f0\i0 .\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf2 2. Semantic Representation & Epistemic Grounding\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Current Audio LLMs:
\f0\b0  Lack an explicit symbolic engine. Meanings are fluid vector coordinates (embeddings) subject to "representation drift" and hallucination. They lack structural logic verification; they observe statistical regularities in training data, but cannot systematically validate the causal or logical structure of an assertion.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Neurobiology:
\f0\b0  The brain bridges continuous sensorimotor representations and symbolic language through structural networks. Motor preparation loops (such as Broca's area and frontoparietal networks) generate internal forward models (efference copies) of speech to predict acoustic outcomes, while temporal-parietal hubs structure semantic relations.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Sanskrit Dar\uc0\u347 ana:
\f0\b0  
\f1\i Navya-Ny\uc0\u257 ya
\f0\i0  provides a highly structured formal metalanguage (
\f1\i Paribh\uc0\u257 \u7779 \u257 
\f0\i0 ) designed to map cognition directly from natural language expressions without losing contextual detail. Every valid cognitive episode (
\f1\i j\'f1\uc0\u257 na
\f0\i0 ) is structured as a 
\f1\i Prak\uc0\u257 ra-Sa\u7747 sarga-Vi\u347 e\u7779 ya
\f0\i0  triad:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1
\f1\i \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	
\f3\i0 \uc0\u9702 
\f1\i 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Vi\uc0\u347 e\u7779 ya:
\f0\i0  The locus or substratum of qualification (the subject).\
\ls2\ilvl1
\f1\i \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	
\f3\i0 \uc0\u9702 
\f1\i 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Prak\uc0\u257 ra:
\f0\i0  The qualifier or qualifier-modifier (the attribute/property).\
\ls2\ilvl1
\f1\i \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	
\f3\i0 \uc0\u9702 
\f1\i 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Sa\uc0\u7747 sarga:
\f0\i0  The exact epistemic relation binding the qualifier to the substrate.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Furthermore, 
\f1\i Ny\uc0\u257 ya
\f0\i0  enforces 
\f1\i \uc0\u346 abda-pram\u257 \u7751 a
\f0\i0  (verbal testimony as an independent, valid source of knowledge). For a sentence to yield valid verbal cognition (
\f1\i \uc0\u346 \u257 bdabodha
\f0\i0 ), it must satisfy four semantic constraints:\uc0\u8232 $$\\text\{\u346 \u257 bdabodha\} \\propto f(\\bar\{A\}k\\bar\{a\}\\dot\{m\}k\\bar\{s\}\\bar\{a\}, \\text\{Yogyat\\=\{a\}\}, \\text\{Sannidhi\}, \\text\{T\\=\{a\}\}tparya)$$\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 II. The Critical Limitations of Purely Textual and Current Multi-Modal Architectures\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 By discarding the acoustic continuum, standard token-based text architectures impose fundamental boundaries on AI safety, reasoning capability, and interpretability.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf2 1. The Erasure of the Acoustic Continuum\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 Text LLMs operate over highly processed, discrete tokens optimized through Byte-Pair Encoding (BPE). This lossy pipeline entirely discards the structural envelope of human speech:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Prosodic & Pragmatic Blindness:
\f0\b0  Text-only strings mask critical cues like fundamental frequency ($F_0$) contours, micro-timing shifts, phase changes, and vocal timbre variations. A single string ("That is brilliant") can signal genuine confirmation, extreme irony, or a question based purely on its intonational trajectory. By stripping this information, text LLMs suffer from severe pragmatic ambiguity, requiring disproportionately large parameter allocations simply to infer social context from textual syntax.\
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Tokenization Discontinuity:
\f0\b0  Text tokenization forces continuous thought into arbitrary sub-word boundaries. This creates a brittle representation layer that lacks the smooth topological properties of continuous time-series audio.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf2 2. Object/Noun Bias vs. Process/Verb-First Realities\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 Western predicate logic and contemporary text LLM token distributions are heavily biased toward a 
\f2\b Noun-First (Substance-Centric)
\f0\b0  worldview. Sentences are parsed as static objects possessing static properties ($P(x)$).\
Bhart\uc0\u7771 hari\'92s 
\f1\i V\uc0\u257 kyapad\u299 ya
\f0\i0  argues that reality is fundamentally a stream of 
\f2\b Actions and Processes (Verb-First)
\f0\b0 . A noun is simply a frozen snapshot of an ongoing action\'97the "womb" or locus where an action temporarily stabilizes.\
Current LLMs struggle with dynamic causal tracking and temporal reasoning precisely because their underlying representations treat the world as a compilation of static entities rather than fluid, intersecting actions. An audio-native architecture captures time, velocity, and duration directly within its input features, providing a natural mathematical vector for process-oriented reasoning.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf2 3. The Lack of Explicit Epistemic Architecture\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 Current models use a single, unified weight matrix to process factual data, logical deductions, conversational fluff, and fabrications. They lack a mechanism to differentiate the 
\f2\b epistemic source
\f0\b0  of a data point.\
When an LLM hallucinates, it is due to the lack of an explicit validation layer to audit the structural soundness of its output against an internal ontology. It cannot verify whether an assertion satisfies the criteria of a valid 
\f1\i Pram\uc0\u257 \u7751 a
\f0\i0  (instrument of true knowledge).\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 III. Next-Generation Inspired Architecture: The Pram\uc0\u257 \u7751 a-ALM\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 To address these limitations, we propose the 
\f2\b Pram\uc0\u257 \u7751 a-ALM
\f0\b0 , a neuro-symbolic multi-modal architecture that instantiates a persistent acoustic field, a verb-centric ontology, and a formal 
\f1\i Navya-Ny\uc0\u257 ya
\f0\i0  verification backend.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

