\f1\i Acoustic Context Network
\f0\i0 . If there is an excessive time delay between consecutive tokens in a phrase, the parser isolates the context windows to prevent erroneous semantic binding.\
\ls4\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
