\f2\b\fs28 \cf2 5. The Epistemic Auditor Layer\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 Before sending tokens to the generation heads or Text-to-Speech (TTS) engine, the constructed 
\f1\i Navya-Ny\uc0\u257 ya
\f0\i0  graph must pass an 
\f2\b Epistemic Audit
\f0\b0 . This layer mimics the classical 
\f1\i Anum\uc0\u257 na-pram\u257 \u7751 a
\f0\i0  (formal five-step inference sequence: 
\f1\i Pa\'f1cavayava-Ny\uc0\u257 ya
\f0\i0 ):\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Pratij\'f1\uc0\u257  (Proposition):
\f0\b0  State the hypothesis to be output.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Hetu (Reason):
\f0\b0  Retrieve the causal foundation from the verified knowledge base.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Ud\uc0\u257 hara\u7751 a (Universal Rule + Example):
\f0\b0  Verify via an internal lookup that the reason universally correlates with the proposition (invariant concomitance or 
\f1\i Vy\uc0\u257 pti
\f0\i0 ).\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Upanaya (Application):
\f0\b0  Confirm the current instance aligns with the universal rule.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	5	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Nigamana (Conclusion):
\f0\b0  Commit the statement as truth.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 If the 
\f1\i Hetu
\f0\i0  or 
\f1\i Vy\uc0\u257 pti
\f0\i0  checks fail or reveal structural loops, the model catches its own logical failure prior to generation. This architecture eliminates statistical hallucinations by anchoring output evaluation within an explicit, verifiable symbolic logic engine.\
